HEADWORD: Nuchal
<hw>Nu"chal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>nucal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or
in the region of, the back, or nape, of the neck; -- applied especially
to the anterior median plate in the carapace of turtles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nuciferous</ent>⟦br⟧
